    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 9th level, you may reroll any one attack roll,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Critical-Hits\" rel=\"nofollow\">critical hit</a>&nbsp;confirmation roll, or level check made to overcome spell resistance. You must decide to use this ability after the first roll is made but before the results are revealed by the GM. You must take the second result, even if it is worse. At 9th level, you can use this ability once per day. At 17th level, you can use this ability twice per day.</p>"
